messages:
It looks like a skating park 🛹, 
 so: is everything sliding? 🧊

Well, I don't know for sure. 
 But please, don't fall! 😆

Also, your enemy has a very funny skin. 
 I don't know why... 
 Is it carnival 🎭 already?

The rhythm of the level will be confusing, 
 and the 3-goal deficit 🥅 
 will not help with that.
So: are you ready for fun? ⛸️❄️
